des: To open this skill say: "Alexa, open p. w. s. assistant". Alexa will then prompt you to say "hello". She will ask you what you need today. After you state what you are looking for, Alexa will then make an API call to Open AI chat GPT 3.5. To ask another question, simply say "hello" or "I have another question" after Alexa finishes the result. Remember to consult a healthcare professional or government guidelines should you have additional concerns about allergies, dietary restrictions or food safety and handling. Responses from AI are not always accurate so please use your best judgement before following the advice of the assistant.
